There has been a breakthrough.
Even though smartphone apps like Fitbit were able to track our activity earlier, they didn’t give us a reason to play sports like this game does.
The new will lose its appeal and use will decrease over time.
However, due to Pokemon’s success, there will be more games that will combine apps and virtual reality with becoming active in the real world, helping many people on the hunt to be more active, fit and healthier.
