American military and intelligence agencies work closely with the Ethiopians to combat terrorist threats beyond the region, in Somalia.
Ethiopia’s economy expanded at a considerable rate.
Its infrastructure has improved dramatically – there is a new pendling train in the capital Addis Ababa.
