After the wiring, you go to bed at your usual time.
In addition to the electrodes on the body, one wears a nose glasses, a chest belt and a sensor on the finger.
In addition, a camera on the ceiling captures the sleeping person.
How can those affected manage the problems?
There are quite a lot of standing screws where you can start for a better sleep.
